  "\[RightAssociation]"}]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.990277922486971*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[251]=",
 CellID->185440758,ExpressionUUID->"541e39e7-83cb-4304-a1c2-f6bb0c7778ce"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Each class lands where the formula predicts: zero for the single photon, one \
for the laser, two for thermal light. The three values chart directly:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"cb5fc039-8e83-47f2-a0ad-abf75c65fb2c"],

