Cell["\<\
The familiar wire-and-gate picture, Hadamard and CNOT chain into the QFT \
block. The same object also draws its computational anatomy, the tensor \
network the engine contracts:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"58547a85-b5c8-4051-8285-962ff81f4bd2"],

