Cell[TextData[{
 "A ",
 Cell[BoxData[
 "Graph"], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
  "5e0e00f0-7e23-48ef-9ca3-0a908819a098"],
 " whose vertices are the gate and state tensors and whose edges are the \
contracted indices: the diagram shows the physics, the network shows the \
computation, and Claim 5 steers the order in which that network is contracted."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e4f99582-6933-4f10-ba43-45b0a1cffd0c"],

Cell["\<\
The same network renders in the dual picture too, as a hypergraph in which \
the roles swap, every index a vertex and every tensor one hyperedge spanning \
its indices:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"692b40e8-a3af-448f-8118-50ddb7b794ce"],

